column5: Wanna go stare at and maybe buy a new fishing lure.  You know the lure I mean... the one that once you know it exists you just can't live without it!  Tried calling the store but just get an endless answering machine that turns french and longggg  Anyone know the store hours?
There closed on Sundays now Chris and I think thru the week they open at 10:30
I know the guys go fishing Sundays this time of year. They spend a lot of time on Quinte for walleye.
I went up there on wednesday i think and they were closed by some stupid time like 6 pm. And open on thurs till 9 or something, that is some weird hours, aint ez for me to get up there too...
